title: Avocado
content: You can eat avocado as you like. For example on a [[toast|avocado.toast]].

title: Toast
content:
This is an avocado toast and it looks really good!

title: Guacamole
content: You can eat guacamole on a toast to make a spiced up version of [[avocado toast|avocado.toast]].
